svg.title: Sheet Music for "The Blackbird (Set Dance)"

text.tspan: Notes: Really interesting tune I stumbled upon, maybe in the Irish repertoire? I can't make much sense
of it yet; each part seems to end in a measure of 2/4 instead of the usual 4/4. Must be to fit
the set-dance form, but I don't know much about that. I have no idea about the chords, either.
